      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "a great and a small; great weights, to buy with them, and small weights, to sell with them, as the Targum of Jonathan paraphrases it. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(y)  \"lapis et lapis\", Montanus, Vatablus, Piscator. ",
